<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Sample response: I can see that there are 3 hundreds, 8 tens, and 2 ones, but one of the tens has been moved over to get more ones. In the algorithm, the 80 and 2 are crossed out to show this. The blocks that are not crossed out show the <m>100 + 10 + 5</m> in the algorithm.</p>
  </solution>


